(1, 'CBD Boxes', 'cbd-boxes', 'Implementing the right packaging solution is an important part of your CBD product marketing strategy. CustomBoxesUS, a great source for CBD boxes, can bring innovations to your brand and create a distinct look that you need to increase sales. Make the right impression with your customers by delivering promised quality and effectiveness. Contact us!', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.6;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We at CustomBoxesUs pride ourselves on\r\nproviding the best custom packaging boxes and services in the industry. There\r\nare no other manufacturers that can match our quality products, an extensive\r\nselection of sizes, and personal attention to detail. We work hard to provide you\r\nwith a high-quality product at a great price! If you\'re looking for a reliable\r\ncompany that is dedicated to bringing you the best custom packaging solutions\r\navailable anywhere then you\'ve come to the right place!</span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'cbd-boxes.webp', '<h1><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Custom CBD BOXES: A unique way to make your cannabis\r\nproducts appealing:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Custom CBD boxes are the ideal\r\npackaging for your products. They come in handy when you want to carry a lot of\r\nstuff with you. And they can also be applicable as gift boxes due to their\r\nattractive appearance and style. We produce custom CBD boxes in different\r\nshapes and sizes. Our creators have been working on custom designs according to\r\nour customers’ needs and requirements in order to serve them better. We offer\r\nfree delivery services as well, so buyers need not worry about any charges or\r\nextra taxes because we will bear all of them.</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Our customization services\r\ninclude:</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:\r\n18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Raw Material</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Sizes and Shapes (varies on\r\nthe product you deal with)</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Custom Designs</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Raw Material:</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">You can get your custom CBD\r\nboxes tailor-made of kraft paper, cardboard, and corrugated material. When you\r\nare going to choose the material, you need to keep in mind the texture. Kraft\r\npaper will give you an elegant and classic sense. Instead, corrugated material\r\nis more durable than kraft paper.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">If the product is not too\r\nsensitive to touch, then cardboard will be a perfect choice as well as they are\r\nmore cost-effective than other materials. The price of cardboard varies\r\naccording to its quality and grade.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Sizes and Shapes:</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">We can customize your sizes\r\nand shapes as per your product requirements. A custom-made product will\r\nincrease the value of your brand. If you choose a small design, you can get it\r\nin a small box. On the other hand, if you are looking for something larger and\r\nmore appealing to look at, then the bigger boxes will give you a greater\r\nappeal.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Custom Designs:</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">We provide free design\r\nservices as well. You can leave any kind of message or logo on your custom-made\r\nCBD boxes. The design and choice of colors will depend on your product, yet one\r\nthing is certain they definitely should be catchy and attractive so that\r\ncustomers would want to buy them all off.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">We can add your logo and\r\nmarking on the </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/cbd-boxes/custom-printed-cbd-packaging-boxes\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">custom printed CBD boxes</span></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\"> to make them look\r\nattractive. Logos, photos, and patterns can be printed on them, as per your\r\ndemand. There is no limit. So you can get all creative.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Make your business more\r\nappealing by making an impact with our custom CBD boxes!</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Advertise your cannabis\r\nbusiness with custom boxes:</span><span style=\"font-size:27.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Custom boxes are the best way\r\nto boost the sales of your cannabis brands. They act as the best promotional\r\ntools and will grab a lot of attention. People like to carry their products in\r\nsomething that looks appealing and doesn’t seem cheap. You will get to engage\r\nmore customers if you print your logo or mark it on your custom CBD boxes. You\r\ncan also choose your desired color, design, printed patterns, and messages in\r\norder to make them appealing to look at and easy to carry around.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Add some touch of flair\r\nwith add-ons:</span><span style=\"