=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Customized packaging is highly\r\ncost-effective, but it also depends on the weight of the product that you want\r\nto protect. The more weight your product has, the costlier it will be for you.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom design:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">When choosing a design, make\r\nsure that not only does it look attractive, but it also protects your food and\r\nbeverage at the same time. Therefore, it is necessary to get a design that\r\nsuits your product.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">The color of the cardboard & finishing:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">If you want to impress\r\ncustomers, then you will have to choose bright colors for your customized food\r\n& beverage boxes. It is important to have your custom food & beverage\r\nboxes finished to be flawless and professional. For example, you can have them\r\nprinted with custom lettering as you prefer.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">The printing options: <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Customizing your food &\r\nbeverage boxes has become a major trend in the market. Therefore, it is\r\nimportant to get some creative ideas when working on the design of your\r\ncustomized food & beverage boxes.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Production time: <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Customized products are\r\nusually more time-consuming in the production process than standard products\r\nbecause of their customization problems. Therefore, it is important to get the\r\nproduction time for your customized food & beverage box when conducting an\r\norder for your product.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Why Choose Us?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">We at CustomBoxesUs love to\r\ndesign beautiful packaging for our customers. We design custom food &\r\nbeverage boxes to suit your needs and taste. We offer some of the most creative\r\ndesigns in the market, for a very reasonable price.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">At CustomBoxesUs, we have an\r\nengaged team of skilled professionals who will work hard to make your product\r\nunique from other products in the market! Customizing Food & Beverage Boxes\r\nis just one more way that we can help you stand out from the rest of your\r\ncompetitors in the marketplace.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: justify;\">FAQs<o:p></o:p></h1>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What are food & beverage boxes?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Food and beverage boxes are\r\nsmall, reusable containers that protect products during manufacturing,\r\nshipping, delivery, and storage.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What is the best size of food and beverage box I should buy?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">It depends on your product.\r\nSome products are small in size and can be placed inside a smaller box while\r\nsome are large. So it is important to know what will fit in your custom food\r\n& beverage box before you decide on the size you need.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Do I need to buy a stock of customized food & beverage boxes?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">N</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">o! You don\'t need to spend more money by buying\r\nmore customizable food & beverage boxes because they are just another type\r\nof packaging material. They are supposed to protect products and store them in\r\nbulk, far from damage. So any bulk amount of boxes for your business will do\r\nthe job.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Do food & beverage boxes come in different sizes and shapes?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">In the food & beverage\r\nindustry, you can choose from a range of food & beverage boxes, from\r\nsmaller to larger sizes. It all depends on your product. If your product is\r\nsmall in size, then you will have to buy smaller ones while if your product is\r\nbig, then you will need large ones to contain them. You can also opt for\r\ncustomized food & beverage boxes if you want a unique design that suits\r\nyour needs.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1, 'Custom food & beverage boxes - Custom Boxes US', 'custom food Boxes, beverage boxes, food & beverage packaging, food packaging boxes,', 'We can provide you with any custom food & beverage boxes you desire, as we have experts to make your business grow with custom designs. Contact us to get your instant quote!', 1, NULL, '2022-03-31 21:57:21', '2022-05-25 23:45:44'),
(5, 'Vape Cartridge Boxes', 'vape-cartridge-boxes', 'Use our FDA Approved Custom Vape Cartridge boxes in order to make sure that your product has a great shelf life. With us, you can customize the packaging of your product and can many customers in a blink of an eye! Contact us!', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;color:#0E101A\">Vapes: A device that makes the next generation\r\nappear cool. Such a thing that can make your appearance cool needs to have\r\nsomething eye-appealing! It\'s sure that you will be able to draw the attention\r\nof every person who enters your store with our Vape Cartridge Boxes! So, why\r\nwait? Contact us today to get your quote ready!<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'vape-cartridge-boxes.webp', '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Vape Cartridge Boxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">CustomBoxesUs is a top leading manufacturer of custom vape\r\ncartridge boxes in the US, producing wholesale boxes in a variety of shapes,\r\nsizes, and styles depending on your specific product needs. Our packaging\r\nsolutions rank among the best in the industry. Your business probably deals\r\nwith vape products, so you know how competitive the market is. Keep an eye on\r\nhow your competitors compete. You will increase your overall product sales by\r\nusing customized vape boxes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">In a sense, vaping is the modern smoking method. The trend of\r\nvaping these days is similar to the trend of cigars and pipes in the past.\r\nBusinesses worldwide are increasing their use of custom printed vape cartridge\r\nboxes since vaping is the new norm. Vapes that are classy and elegant must be\r\npackaged well. As a result, if your vape is not packaged in attractive and\r\nstylish packaging, it will not catch the attention of the customer, thus\r\nresulting in low sales.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Why Vape Cartridge Packaging Boxes Are Important?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Your customer interacts first and foremost with the\r\npackaging. You can\'t expect your item to sell if it isn\'t up to standard and\r\ndoesn\'t appeal to your target audience. Therefore, vape sellers need to know\r\nthat custom vape cartridge boxes play an important role in the market. In the\r\nsame way that social media marketing is vital, custom packaging boxes are\r\nanother important marketing tool that many business owners overlook. Having the\r\nright typography, tones, and an appealing design for your packaging will\r\nimpress your customers. You just won a new customer.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Create Customized Vape Cartridge Boxes to Boost Sales.<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">Packaging is the first thing users see, so custom vape boxes\r\ncan boost sales. Additionally, if you cannot communicate with the customer,\r\nthen your business and you are doomed. Our Custom Printed Vape Packaging Boxes\r\ncan help you avoid this situation once and for all!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h