(6, 'Jewelry Boxes', 'jewelry-boxes', '---', '<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0in; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We at CustomBoxesUs offer Jewelry Packaging\r\nBoxes for all your jewelry. Our boxes and packaging are an essential part of\r\nevery jewelry business, whether you are a retailer or wholesaler. We specialize\r\nin making custom jewelry packaging to suit your business\'s needs, and our boxes\r\nare manufactured with the best quality corrugated available.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>', 'jewelry-boxes.webp', '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Fancy your products with Custom Jewelry Packaging Boxes:<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">It is not just about creating a box and placing the jewelry\r\nin it. Instead, it is about making your customers feel unique. Whether you are\r\nlooking for custom jewelry packaging boxes or a jewelry store display box. You\r\nare sure to find something that fits your brand’s essence. Here at\r\nCustomBoxesUs, we have created many custom boxes for worldwide jewelry brands.\r\nWe understand that each brand has its unique style, so we make sure every\r\nclient gets what they want!<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Here are some of the custom jewelry boxes we have created:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">For Yo