(54, 'Magnetic Closure Rigid Boxes', NULL, '<h1><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Wow, Your customers with Magnetic Closure Rigid Boxes:</span></div>\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></div>\r\n<!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">Custom Rigid\r\nBoxes</span></b></a><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black;mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"> </span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">are\r\nthe perfect way to demonstrate your product to your customers. Although you can\r\nfind a lot of varieties in these boxes, using magnetic closure rigid boxes are\r\nthe ones that can make your customers go crazy! Furthermore, the magnetic\r\nmechanism in the box helps your product to remain intact within the box without\r\ngetting any harm, not only when shipping it but also when storing it!</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">We at CustomBoxesUs can help you to get your boxes\r\nready in an attractive way by providing some unique designs! Our elective\r\nexperts can help you in the journey of making your boxes much more appealing to\r\nthe eye of customers! Imagine that your product is in an adorable-looking box,\r\nand it gets into the hands of your customers, customers who are asking for your\r\nproduct, and suddenly they saw that magnetic box! They will be pretty amazed!\r\nAnd know-how is your product good and what features it includes!</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Customize your box as per your requirement:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">Magnetic boxes can be tailor-made in various sizes and\r\nmaterials, such as cardboard and corrugated, with a variety of customization\r\noptions, such as working with pre-designed text and graphics. It is easy to\r\nslip in your products, as there are no unwanted adhesives or tapes. The\r\nmagnetic closure system locks the case quite tight to resist damage when\r\nshipping. Furthermore, the polished surface can make your product appear more\r\nattractive!</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"> At CustomBoxesUs, you can have your boxes ready\r\nas per your requirement. We use different raw materials to make your packaging\r\npossible. No matter what are your requirements, our experts will make it happen\r\nfor you. We can help you in getting everything done with our prime quality\r\npackaging, which improves the overall look of the product and remains safe and\r\nsound during transportation.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Materials you can use to\r\nmake magnetic closure rigid boxes:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">Custom magnetic rigid boxes can be custom-made out of\r\na variety of materials, but corrugated is the most suitable. It\'s vital to\r\nselect the right material when making a </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes/collapsible-rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">collapsible\r\nrigid boxes</span></b></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black;mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"> or </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes/custom-book-style-rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">book\r\nstyle rigid boxes</span></b></a><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"> like this one. If\r\nyou choose paperboard and fold it by hand to make this box, the edge strength\r\nis not as strong, and it requires additional reinforcement. Durable corrugated\r\ncardboard is the most common material applicable to manufacture magnetic\r\nclosure rigid boxes. There are no set rules when making these boxes.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">Some people like to spray paint the corrugated board\r\nand use colorful contact paper to make it look pretty. You can also wrap the\r\nbox with a plain or patterned cloth or fabric. As long as the box is strong, it\r\nwill work. Therefore, at CustomBoxesUs, you don\'t have to stress about anything\r\nas our experts will guide you in having the best bespoke boxes for your brand!</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Functional Feature of\r\ncustom magnetic boxes:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">The use of magnetic rigid boxes is increasing. These\r\nboxes are used where private information must not be removed from the box and\r\nwhere contents of the box can be removed one by one. Rigid magnetic board or\r\ncorrugated material along with magnet closure allows for a very strong closure\r\nin order to keep documents safe. This magnetic lid keeps its\' hold on the side\r\nof the box but opens easily. The lid also stays attached, so it\'s still visible\r\nafter opening and closing the lid. The top and bottom flaps fold for easy\r\nassembly, feature clear inserts for text and optional tear-off stubs, and your\r\nprinting goes around all four sides for maximum exposure.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Promote your brand with\r\nmagnetic rigid boxes:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style