\nno-minimum-order policy, which has been carefully established by our\r\nspecialists, who have spent years of their lives in the packaging sector, to\r\nmeet your precise quantity needs at affordable costs.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">A Whole Team Of Designers<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Customboxesus\' skilled\r\ndesigners, with their skills and great knowledge in the area of design, support\r\nand empower you to create the boxes like never before and precisely how you\r\nwant them to be, completely free of charge. Our expert engineers are extremely\r\ncompetent and trained. So, they can quickly develop any design for you. Also,\r\nthey will add foil stamping, embossing, and debossing on your request. These\r\nfeatures are perfect to improve the appearance of your mascara liners and\r\nentice consumers to choose yours over others. Our creative designers\'\r\nexperience and years of industry knowledge will provide the finest quality\r\nboxes. Also, they will enable you to go beyond the box with the aesthetics of\r\nyour product. So, they will keep your product in the minds of females for a\r\nlong time.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-he