 font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">    </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Tuck the end boxes.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We make Mailer boxes to\r\nstore many sorts of jewelry. Mailer boxes we provide are strong and may grasp\r\nthe jewelry from the inside by utilizing specific cardboard sheets. Corrugated\r\nmaterial, which contains cardboard layers and a flute layer, is what we use to\r\nmake custom mailer boxes. As a result, mailer boxes can readily lift heavy\r\njewelry.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We utilize bespoke sleeve\r\nboxes to make the jewelry boxes seem very elegant. Custom sleeve boxes are a\r\nparticularly appealing sort of packaging. Because of its distinct style, it\r\ndraws consumers and is ideal for giving a