m bracelet jewelry boxes', 'With the bracelet jewelry boxes, Customboxesus provides, you can package collections of bracelet items of different sizes and styles', 'Custom bracelet jewelry boxes', 'Custom bracelet  jewelry Packaging boxes', 'Custom Printed bracelet jewelry boxes', 'Custom Riged bracelet jewelry boxes', NULL, 1, 6, 1, NULL, '2022-04-01 23:18:25', '2022-06-20 23:18:02'),
(27, 'Custom Macron Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Macron boxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">We at CustomBoxesUs give our best to satisfy our\r\ncustomers. And we have a team of experts that makes your dream packaging a\r\nreality. Macon boxes are well-known to store </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">bakery\r\nproducts</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"> while\r\nallowing consumers to see the items. And we strive to give the best in the\r\npackaging industry. Whether you want to have a box for bakery biscuits, </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes/custom-chocolate-packaging-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">chocolates</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"> and </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes/custom-pastry-packaging-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">pastry</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"> or whether you want to have a\r\nbox for patties, we got your back!</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Not just your daily packaging company, We are your partners.</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">It is our experts\' intention to make you feel wonderful\r\nduring this time of difficulty. Our services include</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">    </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Selection of raw material</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">    </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Colors, Fonts, and style</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">    </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Designs to make it unique</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-h