olors, fonts, and styles:</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">When you tend to work in the business industry like fast-food\r\nor bakery items, it is advisable to have your custom boxes in the color of\r\nyellow or orange. The color of these macron boxes makes people hungry, so if\r\nyou have something unique in mind, you can tell our experts, and they can use\r\nthat color to dye your boxes. Moreover, you can emboss any desired font on your\r\nmacron box to attract more customers to buy your product.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\">In addition to this, you have these boxes in 2 different\r\nstyles such as </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">    </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\">Macron window boxes: Macron\r\nwindow boxes are one of the leading custom packaging options that allow a customer\r\nto see the product before purchasing it. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-