(29, 'Custom Bottle Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Bottle Boxes <o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Whether you are shipping\r\nbeverage containers of beer, cider, wine, or spirits in bulk, we can help. Our\r\ndivider-style cardboard container boxes are ideal for shipping beverage\r\ncontainers. We offer </span><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">customized\r\nbottle boxes</span></a><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";=\"\" color:black\"=\"\"> in sizes from 3x4x12\" to 18x2.5x10.5\" and we also\r\ncarry stock and custom dividers and corrugated packs to meet your individual\r\nneeds.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Customization to make your boxes attractive:</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We can make your boxes with\r\nfull-color printing or have a simple colored logo. We also offer\r\ncustom-designed labels and tags for each of your containers. Hence,