just one color. Our graphic designers are able to\r\ncreate a custom design for you. Find out more about the full line of options\r\navailable for your bottles and your box.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">For your custom bottle boxes, we can assist you with the perfect materials:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">From cardboard movers to\r\nbeer bottles to corrugated inserts, we provide the backing for your bottles.\r\nOur inner packaging is also a perfect choice for your product to make your move\r\neasier. Contact us today for more information.</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Beer and alcohol retail\r\nbusinesses have a unique shipping products to meet their needs. Our products\r\nare custom-made to fit the needs of your business, whether you are shipping\r\nbeer or wine. We enhance your business image at the same time that we keep your\r\npackaging durable and safe. </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">We can customize each box to meet everyone\'s specific needs:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">For our customers, we make\r\nsure that each box is attractive and will not cause any damage if it is shipped\r\nto your customer\'s home or retail store. We also make sure that each box is\r\nsafe for your customers to keep their product in shipment safe </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Whether you are looking for\r\na simple, unbranded box within a price range or a high-quality branded box at\r\nan even higher quality, we can do it all! We offer our customers a great low\r\ncost on each of the custom-made bottle boxes we provide. Our custom bottle\r\nboxes are tailor-made from 100% recycled materials; ensuring that they are\r\ntrendy and eco-friendly in addition to being durable.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style