go to your customer\'s house or retail store.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 36px;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 36px;\"=\"\">FAQs</span></h1><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: windowtext; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 36px;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Q: What is the shipping time?</span><br></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">A: We have worked with many\r\ncustomers throughout the United States to make shipping efficient for your\r\nbusiness. Our products are ready to ship within a few days, even on short\r\nnotice.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Q: Can I get a sample of your product?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"tex