(30, 'Custom Cereal Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Cereal Packaging Boxes <o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Cereals are amongst the\r\nmost popular breakfast in America, therefore it is a must for you to have\r\ncustom cereal boxes for your flavored grains. Why? To showcase your product\r\nmuch better! We at CustomBoxesUs provide the best customization services by\r\nmaintaining a satisfactory level of clients. We are your best choice if you\'re\r\nin need of custom cereal boxes for your brand.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">The journey from raw material to the end product:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Raw materials:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We have a lot of raw\r\nmaterials in sto