We included this option during the checkout process since the logo application\r\nmust be bought for the complete transaction. You may also purchase simple wraps\r\nor wraps with extra choices that are only accessible on product sites.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">For the eCommerce industry,\r\nwe recognize that floral packaging is a marketing technique in and of itself.\r\nIt represents the brand. Hence, we assist our clients in delivering\r\nunforgettable unpacking experiences.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Flower Wraps FOR BUSINESS<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We are introducing our new\r\nflower packaging portfolio, a collection of eCommerce options tailored to the\r\ncut flower and potted plant markets. Our all-paper solutions are guaranteed to\r\nprovide optimal product protection as well as a spectacular unpacking\r\nexperience.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">To manufacture our wraps,\r\nwe employ quality eco-friendly materials and customization options. Your\r\ncreativity is the only limit. So, allow us to make your customized flower wrap\r\nconcept a reality.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What Makes Us Unique Among Our Competitors<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Get to know why people\r\nprefer to hire us.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Quality</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Premium Paper and\r\nEco-Friendly Consumables are among the high-end materials we use.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Excellent Craftsmanship</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">All of our wraps are\r\nhandcrafted by a team of highly skilled craftspeople.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Options for Customization</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Application of a company\r\nlogo, image printing, custom color, bespoke prints, custom sizes, customizable\r\ndesign, and a variety of additional choices are available.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Materials and Tools</span><br></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">To create our wraps, we\r\nemploy cutting-edge manufacturing technology as well as high-quality,\r\neco-friendly, and food-safe materials.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Personalized Approach<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We assist our clients in\r\nbuilding their brands for the long term by providing unique bespoke packaging\r\nsolutions.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Goal<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Your clients will continue\r\nto purchase from you because you care about the quality of your brand, and\r\nthere can be no quality without caring.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Use Of Paper Covers<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Flowers are a wonderful\r\npresent. A bouquet, when tastefully arranged, is ideal for any occasion -\r\nexpressing love, expressing how you feel, or commemorating a significant event.\r\nThankfully, the days of gorgeous flowers being wrapped in cheap cellophane and\r\ntied with a curly ribbon are long gone. That type of wrapping merely destroyed\r\nthe impression, detracting from the flowers\' inherent beauty.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Today\'s most visible trend\r\nin the field of floristry is in gift packaging, specifically bespoke flower\r\nwraps — presenting flowers in stylish cardboard flower wraps. There is a\r\nbewildering assortment of forms, sizes, colors, cover materials, and other\r\nchoices to pick from, enabling you to create each bouquet completely unique,\r\ndoubling the delight that flowers can provide.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">The employment of\r\ncutting-edge production processes and high-quality materials in the development\r\nof our customized flower wraps makes this sort of packaging appropriate for use\r\nby florists, wedding designers, gift items, baking, catering, and other\r\ncompanies in their daily operations.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Our clients can relax\r\nknowing that even the simplest gift or flower arrangement they provide for\r\ntheir customers will be transformed into a kingly surprise when delivered in a\r\nbeautiful bespoke gift wrap.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">High-End Customization<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Consider using our high-end\r\ncustomized flower wraps for your clothing or accessory company. So, take a look\r\nat what our customers are saying about our goods.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Customboxesus offers\r\ncustomizable bulk flower wraps with your logo, eyelets, eyelets + ribbons,\r\ncustom colors, and more choices. We are a Gift wrap Factory that specializes in\r\ncustomized flower wraps and gift packing.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" st