(56, 'Custom Shoulder Rigid Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Give a luxury to your product using shoulder rigid boxes:<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">Over the years we\'ve found that a rigid box can be an\r\nimportant accessory if you\'re giving a gift of jewelry. A luxurious shoulder\r\nrigid box will provide even a small piece with the protection it deserves. We\r\nat CustomBoxesUs have the ability to make your </span><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\"><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">rigid boxes</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"> into pure art! We at CustomBoxesUs understand\r\nthat the presentation is just as important as the gift itself. So we have\r\ncreated a gift box to make the presentation of your gift exceptional!</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">All of our rigid boxes are custom-made to fit your\r\njewellery. Our boxes arrive flat for easy shipping and can be assembled by\r\nhand. We have a large library of images and logos to choose from or you can\r\nupload your own.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">The functionality of\r\nShoulder Rigid Boxes:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">The shoulder rigid box determines the design of the\r\npackaging: 3 panels, 4 sides & flap. It is a mixture of </span><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\"><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/rigid-boxes/custom-two-piece-rigid-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">two\r\npiece rigid boxes</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" \