(67, 'Custom Underwear Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Underwear\r\nPackaging Boxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">A couple of weeks ago, I\r\nwas shopping at the mall and had to stop by a store called \"La Vie en\r\nRose.\" The store\'s name is an indication of its target market: women. It\'s\r\na lingerie store that sells bras, panties, thongs, and other undergarments. I\r\nknow it sounds weird to talk about undergarments on a blog but that\'s what this\r\npost is about - custom underwear packaging boxes.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We\'ve been getting a lot of\r\nrequests for custom underwear packaging boxes lately from companies looking for\r\nan alternative to the standard plastic or paper resealable bags most items are\r\nshipped in these days. Being a huge supporter of using recyclable and/or\r\nbiodegradable material for packaging, I knew that we could provide a more\r\nenvironmentally friendly way to shop lingerie. As a result, we created the\r\nCustom Underwear Packaging Box, which is made out of compostable, biodegradable\r\ncornstarch paper.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">The box itself can be\r\neasily created by printing an image onto the paper and cutting around it.\r\nHowever, being able to print on paper gives us a lot of options in terms of\r\ncustomizing it. Depending on what you want to fit in your packing box, you can\r\nselect from one of five different colors or create something completely custom\r\nwith your logo or company name printed directly on it. In addition, we can\r\nsupply you with either \"cut & fold\" boxes or \"print &\r\nfold\" boxes if you prefer them folded instead of unfolded.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Types of custom Underwear packaging Boxes:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"f