(71, 'Custom Game Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">How To Create A Unique Custom Game Box For Your Board\r\nGame.</span><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">The creative gaming industry has seen a significant\r\nuptick in popularity in recent years, and with that has come a surge in demand\r\nfor custom game boxes. Whether you’re looking to store your collection of games\r\nor want to give your favorite title a unique look. hence, there are plenty of\r\nreasons to consider investing in a custom game box.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">At CustomBoxesUs, we specialize in creating\r\nhigh-quality boxes for all your gaming needs. We offer a wide range of\r\ncustomization options, ensuring that you can create the perfect box. When it\r\ncomes to gaming, one of the best parts is opening up the box and exploring all\r\nof its contents. It\'s like a toy inside a toy, and it just keeps on giving.\r\nUnfortunately, not all games come in nice boxes (see you later, 90% of JRPGs),\r\nand that can be a real downer. Hence, you can now get custom game boxes\r\ntailor-made for your titles, complete with graphic visuals.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Raw Material that\'s best\r\nfor game boxes:</span><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">We use cardboard as our raw material. It\'s one of the\r\nmost cost-effective materials used in game boxes wholesale and has been around\r\nfor decades. Your games will be packaged safely and shipped with care. The\r\nthickness of the cardboard is not uniform across all titles, and it’s often\r\ndifferent by genre. For example, a card game like Magic the Gathering usually\r\nhas lighter boxes, while a board game like Arkham Horror will have heavier\r\nboxes due to its contents.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\">In the event that a game requires assembly, we use\r\ncard sleeves to protect it during shipment. With us, you can get to customize\r\nyour game box. Our customization includes</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 3.75pt 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></p><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Sizing</span></div><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; line-height: 200%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black;=\"\" mso-ansi-language:en-gb\"=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Standard</span></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Custom</span></div></span><p></p></div><p></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><br></span></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">Sizing:</span><o:p></o:p>