(85, 'Custom Take Away Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Take Away\r\nBoxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Takeaway boxes are exactly\r\nwhat they sound like: a box with a takeout spigot on top. They allow businesses\r\nto speed up the process of serving their customers by allowing them to make\r\ntheir own food, but they also allow consumers themselves to get food without\r\nhaving to leave the store. They’re perfect for markets and other places where\r\npeople might have to wait in line for service.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">At customboxesus we\r\nprovide </span><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\"><a href=\"https://www.customboxesus.com/industry/food-beverage-boxes\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\">custom take away boxes</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\"> to the food industry.\r\nThis includes restaurants, cafes, corner markets and anywhere else where people\r\nneed to eat on the go or in a hurry.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Today, custom takeaway\r\nboxes are an integral part of the food industry, and every restaurant has a\r\nunique custom takeaway box for their products. To carry the products inside,\r\nthe boxes have to be sturdy and durable. Protect the product inside the\r\npackaging from external forces and damage. Don\'t leave the packaging behind.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">Most brands and companies\r\noffer takeaway and home delivery services. When a customer comes into your\r\nstore, you can quickly pack custom take away boxes. So the buyer doesn\'t have\r\nto spend valuable time eating while he is eating the food item. </span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Takeaway Boxes for your Brand at Wholesale Prices<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">If you are looking for a\r\ncost-effective solution for your company, buying takeaway boxes at wholesale is\r\nthe best option. Nonetheless, if you are on a tight budget, you should consider\r\nordering bulk takeaway packaging. From CustomboxesUS, you can buy wholesale\r\ntakeaway boxes at a discount. Further, wholesale custom take away boxes are\r\nless expensive than those ordered in low-run quantities.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Take-away boxes that are eco-friendly<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">We use biodegradable\r\nfood-grade materials to manufacture our takeaway boxes. The materials we use\r\nare recyclable, which helps the environment. Customers who understand the\r\nimportance of these materials and want to improve the environment love these\r\nmaterials.</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\"><br></span></h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Various types of materials<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\" helvetica\",sans-serif;=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\";color:black\"=\"\">There are many materials\r\nthat can be used to make takeaway boxes. Today, there are four main types of\r\npackaging available. The four main types are cardboard, kraft paper, corrugated\r\ncardboard, and rigid cardboard. Below are their details:</span><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-st