(96, 'Custom Printed Kraft Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom printed Kraft packaging boxes to help you promote\r\nyour brand better:<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">If you are looking for custom Kraft Packaging Boxes with windows or lids as a gift box, then\r\nSmall Kraft Boxes are the ideal choices. Paper material is a durable material\r\nthat is the ideal material to make these custom-made boxes and to make sure\r\nthey are sturdy enough to hold various goods without having to worry about\r\ncracks appearing in the near future. Moreover, these boxes are available in\r\ndifferent sizes and shapes, making them even more versatile. It can be applied\r\nas gifts, grocery items like fruits or vegetables, and many more. These small\r\nKraft boxes are both eco-friendly and stylish. You can\'t go wrong if you\'re\r\nlooking for something that is both!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We at CustomBoxesUs can help you to provide with best custom\r\nprinted kraft packaging boxes. We offer you different types of boxes for your\r\nneeds and preferences. If you are looking for a box that is sturdy enough to\r\nprotect useful items from harm, then we at CustomBoxesUs have the best\r\nselection of kraft boxes for you. We have many shapes and sizes of boxes that\r\nyou can use to help transport your necessary items such as lotions, cosmetics,\r\nand much more safely.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 107%; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Here\'s what we\r\nprovide in customization:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Sizes and Shapes<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Custom Designs<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 107%; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Sizes and\r\nShapes:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our custom printed small kraft boxes are available in 4\r\nsizes, according to their needs and storage capacity. This custom kraft box is\r\nour most popular. They are useful for small items such as jewelry, scent\r\nbottles, and many more. These boxes can be placed inside bigger boxes in order\r\nto transport such goods safely without any harm. Furthermore, these come with a\r\nwindow that you can use to look at the goods stored inside. However, please\r\nnote that these boxes are not suitable for foods or liquids as the window is\r\nnot waterproof and moisture can seep through it.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 107%; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Designs:<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"