(97, 'Custom Mailer Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Mailer Boxes: Make your brand stand out with customization<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">These\r\ndays customers are opting for products that have something unique that can get\r\ntheir attention. What\'s the first thing that attracts customers when they get\r\nto see a product on an aisle of a mall? It\'s the packaging of the product that\r\nattracts customers to make a purchase of your product. And in business, there\r\nis no better packaging that can surpass every aspect of luring customers, such\r\nas providing a better shipping environment for your product! We at\r\nCustomBoxesUs take pride in the manufacturing of your packaging. Our Custom\r\nMailer Boxes are one of the best packaging solutions that can help you to\r\nattract customers, as well as provide the best shipping experience. It can cut\r\ndown the time it takes for your product to reach its destination. And it can\r\nprovide products that will make it easy to protect from any damage during\r\ntransportation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We\r\nprovide a variety of different styles for you to choose from. We have boxes\r\nthat can withstand extreme weather conditions, such as heat or cold, can\r\nprotect against vibration as well as noise, and also have the capacity to keep\r\nyour products safe while they are in transit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">What do we provide\r\nin customization?<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"