ustom counter display boxes for your brand to stand out in the market. Customize your boxes with CustomBoxesUs and get a lower rate while going wholesale!', 'Custom Counter Display Boxes', 'Custom Counter Display Packging Boxes', 'Custom Counter Display Printed Boxes', 'Custom Counter Display Wholesale Boxes', NULL, 1, 10, 1, NULL, '2022-05-22 16:51:02', '2022-06-21 13:37:30'),
(101, 'Halloween Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Custom Printed\r\nHalloween Packaging\r\nBoxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1><div style=\"line-height: 1.8;\"><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">For\r\nthe past few years, Halloween has become a worldwide phenomenon. Ghost Costumes\r\nand masks come in many shapes, sizes, and colors. In addition, boxes containing\r\nHalloween-themed freight items go out as gifts. Many companies produce and\r\nprovide these masks, costumes, and gift items in custom printed Halloween\r\npackaging boxes. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8;\">\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">These\r\nproducts go together if the consumer finds them to be suitable. By storing the\r\nrequired products in odd packaging boxes, you can excite your customers.\r\nHalloween custom boxes are available from CustomBoxesUs with a lot of different\r\ndisplays. These boxes are available in all shapes and sizes. By printing\r\nghostly images, they are highly appealing. </span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198);\">Why You Need A Bewitching Box? <o:p></o:p></span></h2></div><div style=\"line-height: 1.8;\"><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">All\r\ncountries celebrate different holidays throughout the year. Before the event\r\nbegins, companies launch several related products to promote the event. The\r\nintroduction of your product into the market certainly requires a considerable\r\namount of work. Making your product is not enough. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;