(102, 'Face Mask Packaging Boxes', NULL, '<h1 style=\"text-align: justify; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 132, 198); font-family: Helvetica;\">Custom Printed Face Mask Packaging Boxes<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">In\r\nrecent days, severe epidemics have afflicted the entire globe. People are\r\nwearing masks to shield their faces against the transmission of this disease.\r\nTo prevent disease, everyone keeps their distance from other human beings. Face\r\nmasks are readily available everywhere because of the increased demand caused\r\nby this virus. Additionally to the facial masks, there are now also custom-made\r\nboxes available.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Several\r\npackaging companies offer high-quality boxes to protect face masks against\r\ndamage. As a result, our company offers environmentally friendly packaging for\r\na variety of different products. Face masks are packaged in a cardboard box\r\nthat guarantees their protection. Hence, it is possible to customize the box\r\nshape and size depending on the number of masks that will fit inside.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.8;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">These\r\ncustom printed face mask packaging boxes typically consist of cardboard, which\r\nallows them to be tailored to your specifications. So, it is possible to store\r\nmultiple masks in one box with three-layer custom printed mask boxes. These\r\ntypes of boxes offer a variety of customization options that help you expand\r\nsales of the product in general.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span><